{"tid":721743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆料智庫大有來頭 《金融恐慌》已呈中央","createTime":"2018-06-29T01:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T03:40:58.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2fbe08e2ad64c2d3ab393bc8407de53b1b257574","tid":721743,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T01:54:53.000Z","msg":"這次撰寫《警惕中國出現金融恐慌》報告的國家金融與發展實驗室（下稱實驗室），原來大有來頭，是中央批准成立的首批國家級高端智庫。據悉，該報告用於機構內部討論，亦已上呈中央。消息稱，實驗室定期發發佈研究報告是公開的，但這份報告不同以往，絕不尋常。<br />\n<br />\n繼續睇：<br />\n【刪報告「愚民」】國家智庫洩密：中國瀕爆金融恐慌（ <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Ktebx0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Ktebx0&d=IhhpZRtuF5vgy5gBgPYU3JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1d862138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Ktebx0</a> ）<br />\n【面臨破產】山東民企負債百億 國資拿73億打救（ <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2lDuI3f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lDuI3f&d=IhhpZRtuF5vgy5gBgPYU3JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=02d65147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2lDuI3f</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n實驗室成立於2005年，為中國社會科學院所支持的國家級智庫。該報告由實驗室理事長、中國社會科學院學部委員李揚、實驗室副主任殷劍峰、研究員尹中立及中國社學院經濟學博士李拉亞等合作撰寫。其中現年67歲的李揚，人民大學財金系畢業，博士學歷，現任中國社會科學院金融研究所所長、研究員，博士生導師；兼任中國金融學會副會長、中國財政學會常務理事、中國國際金融學會常務理事、中國城市金融學會常務理事。李的學術專長為金融學、財政學、宏觀經濟。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180629/58375735\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180629%2F58375735&d=IhhpZRtuF5vgy5gBgPYU3JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=86cb0ee6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180629%2F58375735&h=010be43e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180629/58375735</a>"},{"pid":"90b0fb7106d055c7df6492e1c89f80412ecdcce4","tid":721743,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:03:46.000Z","msg":"大鳴大放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6017339d8915d084283a6e029d4eec6aaa5ea6a","tid":721743,"uid":39855,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:09:11.000Z","msg":"呢D智庫一街都係，首先佢夠唔夠膽講真話先！"},{"pid":"db576de91cdb080fbf582921de12497ee1f733d9","tid":721743,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:16:19.000Z","msg":"點解呢排咁多洩密 中央內部決定又流出 保密文件又流出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a0f551a8f82b887d2431f186e35b4eb9f92c59","tid":721743,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6017339d8915d084283a6e029d4eec6aaa5ea6a","tid":721743,"uid":39855,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:09:11.000Z","msg":"呢D智庫一街都係，首先佢夠唔夠膽講真話先！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:41:20.000Z","msg":"冇運行架咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568fe3b278ba4a8e094d514e879cf9ecad15b9cd","tid":721743,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:47:50.000Z","msg":"呢個世紀係屬於中國嘅世紀，名叫&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">支爆新世紀</span></span>"},{"pid":"5b4ddd12a463abb1d67ae7a63e9aa65e4e41f314","tid":721743,"uid":162906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:03:09.000Z","msg":"爆料 : 中國成最大贏家"},{"pid":"f1d8babef2446e3270525146ac1f93887629aa69","tid":721743,"uid":30169,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"568fe3b278ba4a8e094d514e879cf9ecad15b9cd","tid":721743,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:47:50.000Z","msg":"呢個世紀係屬於中國嘅世紀，名叫&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\